&lt;p&gt;This isn&#39;t a role for someone who wants a playbook. It&#39;s for someone who can write one - for a game that&#39;s breaking new ground, for an audience we&#39;re still learning about, in a market that rewards boldness over convention.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3&gt;&lt;strong&gt;What You’ll Achieve:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/h3&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the game economy across multiple interconnected systems ( progression, monetization, resource flows ) and ensure long-term health and commercial viability.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Drive product direction by translating strategic hypotheses into concrete decisions, specifications, and shipped features.&lt;/li&gt;
