&lt;li&gt;Validate soft launch performance through disciplined experimentation.&amp;nbsp; A/B tests, cohort analysis, and KPI deep-dives are deeply understood, and you make clear recommendations on global launch readiness.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Take real decisions under real pressure. You&#39;ll own the call on what to ship, what to cut, and when we&#39;re ready to scale.&lt;/li&gt;
