&lt;li&gt;Ensure accurate, timely payroll processing in dedicated locations, in coordination with external and internal partners.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Manage invoicing and accounting activities for multiple international entities, ensuring compliance with local GAAP and statutory requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Maintain accurate financial records and support audit processes.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assist in the preparation of financial statements and reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with cross-functional teams to improve financial processes and systems.&lt;/li&gt;
